Interface Closeable

  • All Superinterfaces:
    AutoCloseable
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    Closeable.Set, Connection

    public interface Closeable
extends AutoCloseable
    An extension of AutoCloseable chiefly to eliminate the checked exception thrown by close(). React resources generally do not encounter failure during closure, thus the checked exception is a needless burden to pass on to callers.
